cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG 

The paper deals with interactive image retrieval using natural language feedback, which involves aspects of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of reinforcement learning (RL) to formulate the task of dialog-based interactive image retrieval also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the RL sub-category (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of a user simulator, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) tasks, which could also place it in the cs.IR sub-category.
